Kestrel's Ride is a game where you are trying to get to the mortal plains by collecting enough souls to get through the gates of hell. The Angels know of your plan and are trying to stop you. unfortunately for them you are far to powerful and can not be stopped. They will make a great sacrifice. However look out for the falling angels they will take away some of the souls you collected. You will need enough souls to get through the gate or else you'll just smash into it.

Controls WASD to move and 'N' to start a new game.

Hit the angels to collect there souls. You need to fill the bar on the top of the screen before hitting the gate.

Angel types:

White : worth 1 soul;
Blue  : worth 3 souls;

Fallen : takes 2 souls from you;

Note: there is no audio it's not a bug.

